We would stay here again, if you want more luxury it is not for you, if you want a clean safe place and conveniently located for parks then its perfect!	The TV had premium HBO channels (perfect for after a hectic day at the parks).	We booked with first choice and this seems to be there most budget hotel.............if you want better you'll have to pay for it i suppose, We wanted a cheap base to enjoy the local attractions but with that we also got a nice comfortable hotel room in a nice quiet area and everything was fineeeeeeeee.	The rooms were clean, quiet, had HBO, and good air conditioning.